         MACRO
         CNTSRCH &ITER
         LCLA  &A
.*  EACH DOUBLE WORD OF THE DSECT DESCRIBES A COUNT OR SEARCH ARGUMENT.
.*  NORMALLY, SRCHRG HAS THE ADDRESS OF SRCHARG0.  THE SINGLE MACRO
.*  ARGUMENT, &ITER, SPECIFIES THE HIGHEST ITERATION DESIRED.  THUS
.*  CNTSRCH 3 WILL GENERATE ITERATIONS BEGINNING SRCHARG0, SRCHARG1
.*  SRCHARG2, SRCHARG3.
CNTSRCH  DSECT
.BEGIN   ANOP
SRCHARG&A  DS  0F
SRCHCC&A   DS  CL2
SRCHHH&A   DS  CL2
FCOUNT&A   DS  0F
SRCHR&A    DS  X
CNTKEY&A   DS  X
CNTDATA&A  DS  0CL2,C
SRCHCOD&A  DS  X
&A       SETA  &A+1
         SPACE
         AIF   (&A LE &ITER).BEGIN
         MEND
